                <th>Strengths</th>
                <th>Typical fit</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Looker</strong></td>
                <td>Strong semantic layer (LookML), governance-friendly, embedded analytics</td>
                <td>Mid-to-large enterprises wanting governed self-service</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Microsoft Power BI</strong></td>
                <td>Ubiquitous in Microsoft-anchored estates, strong report-authoring</td>
